  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db4\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dbb\u0da7\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d8b\u0daf\u0dc0\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Foreign countries assist in our work",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has said that the United States and other countries are ready to help Sri Lanka after presenting the program to build the country.",
        "The Prime Minister said that the country building program is being prepared with the involvement of the Cabinet of Ministers and that the program could be presented within the next two to three weeks.",
        "Speaking to the media, the Prime Minister further said that foreign aid is needed to revive the collapsing economy in 2023 and revive the country by 2024 and 2025.",
        "The Prime Minister also said that the present program to build the country has been accepted by the countries that have held discussions in recent days.",
        "The Prime Minister also said that the government would fully support the home gardening programs of the Samagi Jana Balawegaya and the Janatha Vimukthi Peramuna.",
        "The Prime Minister said that at present all the state corporations were making losses and none of them could be sustained and if anyone had a better plan than his own, he should submit it to Parliament."
      ],
